{
  "video_id": "_mLeSPk3ddE",
  "title": "Katherine Fulton: You are the future of philanthropy",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 18330.0,
      "end_time": 22330.0,
      "text": "I want to help you re-perceive what philanthropy is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 22330.0,
      "end_time": 24330.0,
      "text": "what it could be,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 24330.0,
      "end_time": 26330.0,
      "text": "and what your relationship to it is."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 26330.0,
      "end_time": 29330.0,
      "text": "And in doing that, I want to offer you a vision,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 29330.0,
      "end_time": 32330.0,
      "text": "an imagined future, if you will,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 32330.0,
      "end_time": 36330.0,
      "text": "of how, as the poet Seamus Heaney has put it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 36330.0,
      "end_time": 38330.0,
      "text": "\"Once in a lifetime"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 38330.0,
      "end_time": 42330.0,
      "text": "the longed-for tidal wave of justice can rise up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 42330.0,
      "end_time": 46330.0,
      "text": "and hope and history rhyme.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 46330.0,
      "end_time": 50330.0,
      "text": "I want to start with these word pairs here."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 50330.0,
      "end_time": 54330.0,
      "text": "We all know which side of these we&#39;d like to be on."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 54330.0,
      "end_time": 57330.0,
      "text": "When philanthropy was reinvented a century ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 57330.0,
      "end_time": 60330.0,
      "text": "when the foundation form was actually invented,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 60330.0,
      "end_time": 64330.0,
      "text": "they didn&#39;t think of themselves on the wrong side of these either."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 64330.0,
      "end_time": 66330.0,
      "text": "In fact they would never have thought of themselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 66330.0,
      "end_time": 69330.0,
      "text": "as closed and set in their ways,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 69330.0,
      "end_time": 71330.0,
      "text": "as slow to respond to new challenges,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 71330.0,
      "end_time": 73330.0,
      "text": "as small and risk-averse."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 73330.0,
      "end_time": 76330.0,
      "text": "And in fact they weren&#39;t. They were reinventing charity in those times,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 76330.0,
      "end_time": 79330.0,
      "text": "what Rockefeller called \"the business of benevolence.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 79330.0,
      "end_time": 81330.0,
      "text": "But by the end of the 20th century,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 81330.0,
      "end_time": 84330.0,
      "text": "a new generation of critics and reformers"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 84330.0,
      "end_time": 88330.0,
      "text": "had come to see philanthropy just this way."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 88330.0,
      "end_time": 90330.0,
      "text": "The thing to watch for"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 90330.0,
      "end_time": 92330.0,
      "text": "as a global philanthropy industry comes about --"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 92330.0,
      "end_time": 95330.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s exactly what is happening --"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 95330.0,
      "end_time": 97330.0,
      "text": "is how the aspiration is to flip"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 97330.0,
      "end_time": 99330.0,
      "text": "these old assumptions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 99330.0,
      "end_time": 101330.0,
      "text": "for philanthropy to become open and big"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 101330.0,
      "end_time": 104330.0,
      "text": "and fast and connected, in service of the long term."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 104330.0,
      "end_time": 106330.0,
      "text": "This entrepreneurial energy"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 106330.0,
      "end_time": 108330.0,
      "text": "is emerging from many quarters."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 108330.0,
      "end_time": 111330.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s driven and propelled forward by new leaders, like many of the people here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 111330.0,
      "end_time": 114330.0,
      "text": "by new tools, like the ones we&#39;ve seen here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 114330.0,
      "end_time": 116330.0,
      "text": "and by new pressures."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 116330.0,
      "end_time": 119330.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve been following this change for quite a while now, and participating in it."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 119330.0,
      "end_time": 121330.0,
      "text": "This report is our main public report."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 121330.0,
      "end_time": 123330.0,
      "text": "What it tells is the story of how today"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 123330.0,
      "end_time": 125330.0,
      "text": "actually could be as historic"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 125330.0,
      "end_time": 127330.0,
      "text": "as 100 years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 127330.0,
      "end_time": 130329.0,
      "text": "What I want to do is share some of the coolest things"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 130330.00000000001,
      "end_time": 132330.0,
      "text": "that are going on with you."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 132330.0,
      "end_time": 135330.0,
      "text": "And as I do that, I&#39;m not going to dwell much"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 135330.0,
      "end_time": 139330.0,
      "text": "on the very large philanthropy that everybody already knows about --"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 139330.0,
      "end_time": 142330.0,
      "text": "the Gates or the Soros or the Google."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 142330.0,
      "end_time": 145330.0,
      "text": "Instead, what I want to do"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 145330.0,
      "end_time": 149330.0,
      "text": "is talk about the philanthropy of all of us:"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 149330.0,
      "end_time": 151330.0,
      "text": "the democratization of philanthropy."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 151330.0,
      "end_time": 153330.0,
      "text": "This is a moment in history when the average person"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 153330.0,
      "end_time": 156330.0,
      "text": "has more power than at any time."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 156330.0,
      "end_time": 159330.0,
      "text": "What I&#39;m going to do is look at five categories of experiments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 159330.0,
      "end_time": 164330.0,
      "text": "each of which challenges an old assumption of philanthropy."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 164330.0,
      "end_time": 168330.0,
      "text": "The first is mass collaboration, represented here by Wikipedia."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 168330.0,
      "end_time": 170330.0,
      "text": "Now, this may surprise you."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 170330.0,
      "end_time": 175330.0,
      "text": "But remember, philanthropy is about giving of time and talent, not just money."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 175330.0,
      "end_time": 179330.0,
      "text": "Clay Shirky, that great chronicler of everything networked,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 179330.0,
      "end_time": 181330.0,
      "text": "has captured the assumption that this challenges"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 181330.0,
      "end_time": 183330.0,
      "text": "in such a beautiful way."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 183330.0,
      "end_time": 185330.0,
      "text": "He said, \"We have lived in this world"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 185330.0,
      "end_time": 187330.0,
      "text": "where little things are done for love"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 187330.0,
      "end_time": 189330.0,
      "text": "and big things for money."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 189330.0,
      "end_time": 191330.0,
      "text": "Now we have Wikipedia."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 191330.0,
      "end_time": 195330.0,
      "text": "Suddenly big things can be done for love.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 195330.0,
      "end_time": 198330.0,
      "text": "Watch, this spring, for Paul Hawken&#39;s new book --"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 198330.0,
      "end_time": 200330.0,
      "text": "Author and entrepreneur many of you may know about."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 200330.0,
      "end_time": 202330.0,
      "text": "The book is called \"Blessed Unrest.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 202330.0,
      "end_time": 204330.0,
      "text": "And when it comes out, a series of wiki sites"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 204330.0,
      "end_time": 207330.0,
      "text": "under the label WISER, are going to launch at the same time."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 207330.0,
      "end_time": 209330.0,
      "text": "WISER stands for World Index"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 209330.0,
      "end_time": 212330.0,
      "text": "for Social and Environmental Responsibility."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 212330.0,
      "end_time": 214330.0,
      "text": "WISER sets out to document, link and empower"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 214330.0,
      "end_time": 217330.0,
      "text": "what Paul calls the largest movement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 217330.0,
      "end_time": 219330.0,
      "text": "and fastest-growing movement in human history:"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 219330.0,
      "end_time": 222330.0,
      "text": "humanity&#39;s collective immune response"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 222330.0,
      "end_time": 224330.0,
      "text": "to today&#39;s threats."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 224330.0,
      "end_time": 228330.0,
      "text": "Now, all of these big things for love -- experiments --"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 228330.0,
      "end_time": 230330.0,
      "text": "aren&#39;t going to take off."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 230330.0,
      "end_time": 232330.0,
      "text": "But the ones that do"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 232330.0,
      "end_time": 234330.0,
      "text": "are going to be the biggest, the most open,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 234330.0,
      "end_time": 238330.0,
      "text": "the fastest, the most connected form of philanthropy in human history."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 238330.0,
      "end_time": 241330.0,
      "text": "Second category is online philanthropy marketplaces."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 241330.0,
      "end_time": 243330.0,
      "text": "This is, of course, to philanthropy"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 243330.0,
      "end_time": 247330.0,
      "text": "what eBay and Amazon are to commerce."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 247330.0,
      "end_time": 250330.0,
      "text": "Think of it as peer-to-peer philanthropy."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 250330.0,
      "end_time": 253330.0,
      "text": "And this challenges yet another assumption,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 253330.0,
      "end_time": 257330.0,
      "text": "which is that organized philanthropy is only for the very wealthy."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 257329.0,
      "end_time": 260329.0,
      "text": "Take a look, if you haven&#39;t, at DonorsChoose."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 260329.0,
      "end_time": 263330.0,
      "text": "Omidyar Network has made a big investment in DonorsChoose."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 263330.0,
      "end_time": 265330.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s one of the best known of these new marketplaces"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 265330.0,
      "end_time": 267330.0,
      "text": "where a donor can go straight into a classroom"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 267330.0,
      "end_time": 270330.0,
      "text": "and connect with what a teacher says they need."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 270330.0,
      "end_time": 272330.0,
      "text": "Take a look at Changing the Present,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 272330.0,
      "end_time": 275330.0,
      "text": "started by a TEDster, next time you need a wedding present or a holiday present."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 275330.0,
      "end_time": 277330.0,
      "text": "GiveIndia is for a whole country."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 277330.0,
      "end_time": 279330.0,
      "text": "And it goes on and on."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 279330.0,
      "end_time": 282330.0,
      "text": "The third category is represented by Warren Buffet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 282330.0,
      "end_time": 284330.0,
      "text": "which I call aggregated giving."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 284330.0,
      "end_time": 287330.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not just that Warren Buffet was so amazingly generous"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 287330.0,
      "end_time": 289330.0,
      "text": "in that historic act last summer."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 289330.0,
      "end_time": 291330.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s that he challenged another assumption,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 291330.0,
      "end_time": 293330.0,
      "text": "that every giver should have his or her own"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 293330.0,
      "end_time": 295330.0,
      "text": "fund or foundation."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 295330.0,
      "end_time": 299330.0,
      "text": "There are now, today, so many new funds"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 299330.0,
      "end_time": 301330.0,
      "text": "that are aggregating giving and investing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 301330.0,
      "end_time": 304330.0,
      "text": "bringing together people"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 304330.0,
      "end_time": 306330.0,
      "text": "around a common goal, to think bigger."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 306330.0,
      "end_time": 310330.0,
      "text": "One of the best known is Acumen Fund, led by Jacqueline Novogratz,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 310330.0,
      "end_time": 312330.0,
      "text": "a TEDster who got a big boost here at TED."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 312330.0,
      "end_time": 315330.0,
      "text": "But there are many others: New Profit in Cambridge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 315330.0,
      "end_time": 318330.0,
      "text": "New School&#39;s Venture Fund in Silicon Valley,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 318330.0,
      "end_time": 321330.0,
      "text": "Venture Philanthropy Partners in Washington,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 321330.0,
      "end_time": 323330.0,
      "text": "Global Fund for Women in San Francisco."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 323330.0,
      "end_time": 325330.0,
      "text": "Take a look at these."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 325330.0,
      "end_time": 328330.0,
      "text": "These funds are to philanthropy"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 328330.0,
      "end_time": 333330.0,
      "text": "what venture capital, private equity, and eventually mutual funds"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 333330.0,
      "end_time": 335330.0,
      "text": "are to investing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 335330.0,
      "end_time": 337330.0,
      "text": "but with a twist --"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 337330.0,
      "end_time": 342330.0,
      "text": "because often a community forms around these funds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 342330.0,
      "end_time": 345330.0,
      "text": "as it has at Acumen and other places."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 345330.0,
      "end_time": 348330.0,
      "text": "Now, imagine for a second"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 348330.0,
      "end_time": 351330.0,
      "text": "these first three types of experiments:"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 351330.0,
      "end_time": 354330.0,
      "text": "mass collaboration, online marketplaces, aggregated giving."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 354330.0,
      "end_time": 357330.0,
      "text": "And understand how they help us re-perceive"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 357330.0,
      "end_time": 359330.0,
      "text": "what organized philanthropy is."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 359330.0,
      "end_time": 362330.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not about foundations necessarily; it&#39;s about the rest of us."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 362330.0,
      "end_time": 367330.0,
      "text": "And imagine the mash-up, if you will, of these things, in the future,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 367330.0,
      "end_time": 369330.0,
      "text": "when these things come together in the experiments of the future --"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 369330.0,
      "end_time": 372330.0,
      "text": "imagine that somebody puts up, say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 372330.0,
      "end_time": 374330.0,
      "text": "100 million dollars"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 374330.0,
      "end_time": 376330.0,
      "text": "for an inspiring goal --"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 376330.0,
      "end_time": 379330.0,
      "text": "there were 21 gifts of 100 million dollars or more in the US last year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 379330.0,
      "end_time": 382330.0,
      "text": "not out of the question --"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 382330.0,
      "end_time": 385330.0,
      "text": "but only puts it up if it&#39;s matched"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 385330.0,
      "end_time": 388330.0,
      "text": "by millions of small gifts from around the globe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 388330.0,
      "end_time": 390330.0,
      "text": "thereby engaging lots of people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 390330.0,
      "end_time": 392330.0,
      "text": "and building visibility and engaging people"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 392330.0,
      "end_time": 395330.0,
      "text": "in the goal that&#39;s stated."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 395330.0,
      "end_time": 397330.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to look quickly at the fourth and fifth categories,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 397330.0,
      "end_time": 401330.0,
      "text": "which are innovation, competitions and social investing."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 401330.0,
      "end_time": 405330.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re betting a visible competition, a prize,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 405330.0,
      "end_time": 408330.0,
      "text": "can attract talent and money to some of the most difficult issues,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 408330.0,
      "end_time": 411330.0,
      "text": "and thereby speed the solution."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 411330.0,
      "end_time": 414330.0,
      "text": "This tackles yet another assumption,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 414330.0,
      "end_time": 416330.0,
      "text": "that the giver and the organization is at the center,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 416330.0,
      "end_time": 419330.0,
      "text": "as opposed to putting the problem at the center."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 419330.0,
      "end_time": 421330.0,
      "text": "You can look to these innovators"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 421330.0,
      "end_time": 424330.0,
      "text": "to help us especially with things that require"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 424330.0,
      "end_time": 428330.0,
      "text": "technological or scientific solution."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 428330.0,
      "end_time": 432330.0,
      "text": "That leaves the final category, social investing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 432330.0,
      "end_time": 434330.0,
      "text": "which is really, anyway, the biggest of them all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 434330.0,
      "end_time": 437330.0,
      "text": "represented here by Xigi.net."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 437330.0,
      "end_time": 441330.0,
      "text": "And this, of course, tackles the biggest assumption of all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 441330.0,
      "end_time": 443330.0,
      "text": "that business is business,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 443330.0,
      "end_time": 447330.0,
      "text": "and philanthropy is the vehicle of people who want to create change in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 447330.0,
      "end_time": 449330.0,
      "text": "Xigi is a new community site"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 449330.0,
      "end_time": 451330.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s built by the community,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 451330.0,
      "end_time": 455330.0,
      "text": "linking and mapping this new social capital market."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 455330.0,
      "end_time": 457330.0,
      "text": "It lists already 1,000 entities"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 457330.0,
      "end_time": 461330.0,
      "text": "that are offering debt and equity for social enterprise."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 461330.0,
      "end_time": 464330.0,
      "text": "So we can look to these innovators"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 464330.0,
      "end_time": 468330.0,
      "text": "to help us remember"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 468330.0,
      "end_time": 471330.0,
      "text": "that if we can leverage even a small amount of the capital"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 471330.0,
      "end_time": 473330.0,
      "text": "that seeks a return,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 473330.0,
      "end_time": 478330.0,
      "text": "the good that can be driven could be astonishing."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 478330.0,
      "end_time": 480330.0,
      "text": "Now, what&#39;s really interesting here"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 480330.0,
      "end_time": 484330.0,
      "text": "is that we&#39;re not thinking our way"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 484330.0,
      "end_time": 486330.0,
      "text": "into a new way of acting;"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 486330.0,
      "end_time": 489330.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re acting our way into a new way of thinking."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 489330.0,
      "end_time": 492330.0,
      "text": "Philanthropy is reorganizing itself"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 492330.0,
      "end_time": 494330.0,
      "text": "before our very eyes."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 494330.0,
      "end_time": 498330.0,
      "text": "And even though all of the experiments and all of the big givers"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 498330.0,
      "end_time": 501330.0,
      "text": "don&#39;t yet fulfill this aspiration,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 501330.0,
      "end_time": 503330.0,
      "text": "I think this is the new zeitgeist:"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 503330.0,
      "end_time": 506330.0,
      "text": "open, big, fast, connected,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 506330.0,
      "end_time": 508330.0,
      "text": "and, let us also hope, long."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 508330.0,
      "end_time": 512329.0,
      "text": "We have got to realize that it is going to take a long time to do these things."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 512330.00000000006,
      "end_time": 515330.00000000006,
      "text": "If we don&#39;t develop the stamina to stick with things --"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 515330.00000000006,
      "end_time": 518330.00000000006,
      "text": "whatever it is you pick, stick with it --"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 518330.00000000006,
      "end_time": 522330.00000000006,
      "text": "all of this stuff is just going to be, you know, a fad."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 522330.00000000006,
      "end_time": 524330.0,
      "text": "But I&#39;m really hopeful."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 524330.0,
      "end_time": 526330.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m hopeful because it&#39;s not only philanthropy"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 526330.0,
      "end_time": 528330.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s reorganizing itself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 528330.0,
      "end_time": 531330.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s also whole other portions of the social sector,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 531330.0,
      "end_time": 534330.0,
      "text": "and of business,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 534330.0,
      "end_time": 537330.0,
      "text": "that are busy challenging \"business as usual.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 537330.0,
      "end_time": 540330.0,
      "text": "And everywhere I go, including here at TED,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 540330.0,
      "end_time": 544330.0,
      "text": "I feel that there is a new moral hunger"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 544330.0,
      "end_time": 546330.0,
      "text": "that is growing."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 546330.0,
      "end_time": 548330.0,
      "text": "What we&#39;re seeing is people really wrestling"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 548330.0,
      "end_time": 551330.0,
      "text": "to describe what is this new thing that&#39;s happening."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 551330.0,
      "end_time": 553330.0,
      "text": "Words like \"philanthrocapitalism,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 553330.0,
      "end_time": 555330.0,
      "text": "and \"natural capitalism,\" and \"philanthroentrepreneur,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 555330.0,
      "end_time": 557330.0,
      "text": "and \"venture philanthropy.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 557330.0,
      "end_time": 559330.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t have a language for it yet."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 559330.0,
      "end_time": 561330.0,
      "text": "Whatever we call it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 561330.0,
      "end_time": 563330.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s new, it&#39;s beginning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 563330.0,
      "end_time": 567330.0,
      "text": "and I think it&#39;s gong to quite significant."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 567330.0,
      "end_time": 569330.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s where my imagined future comes in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 569330.0,
      "end_time": 573330.0,
      "text": "which I am going to call the social singularity."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 573330.0,
      "end_time": 576330.0,
      "text": "Many of you will realize that I&#39;m ripping a bit off of the science fiction writer"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 576330.0,
      "end_time": 579330.0,
      "text": "Vernor Vinge&#39;s notion of a technological singularity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 579330.0,
      "end_time": 581330.0,
      "text": "where a number of trends accelerate and converge"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 581330.0,
      "end_time": 585330.0,
      "text": "and come together to create, really, a shockingly new reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 585330.0,
      "end_time": 588330.0,
      "text": "It may be that the social singularity"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 588330.0,
      "end_time": 592330.0,
      "text": "ahead is the one that we fear the most:"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 592330.0,
      "end_time": 594330.0,
      "text": "a convergence of catastrophes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 594330.0,
      "end_time": 596330.0,
      "text": "of environmental degradation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 596330.0,
      "end_time": 598330.0,
      "text": "of weapons of mass destruction, of pandemics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 598330.0,
      "end_time": 600330.0,
      "text": "of poverty."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 600330.0,
      "end_time": 602330.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s because"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 602330.0,
      "end_time": 606330.0,
      "text": "our ability to confront the problems that we face"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 606330.0,
      "end_time": 609330.0,
      "text": "has not kept pace with our ability to create them."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 609330.0,
      "end_time": 611330.0,
      "text": "And as we&#39;ve heard here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 611330.0,
      "end_time": 613330.0,
      "text": "it is no exaggeration to say"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 613330.0,
      "end_time": 616330.0,
      "text": "that we hold the future of our civilization in our hands"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 616330.0,
      "end_time": 619330.0,
      "text": "as never before."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 619330.0,
      "end_time": 622330.0,
      "text": "The question is, is there a positive social singularity?"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 622330.0,
      "end_time": 624330.0,
      "text": "Is there a frontier for us"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 624330.0,
      "end_time": 627330.0,
      "text": "of how we live together?"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 627330.0,
      "end_time": 629330.0,
      "text": "Our future doesn&#39;t have to be imagined."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 629330.0,
      "end_time": 634330.0,
      "text": "We can create a future where hope and history rhyme."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 634330.0,
      "end_time": 636330.0,
      "text": "But we have a problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 636330.0,
      "end_time": 640330.0,
      "text": "Our experience to date, both individually and collectively,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 640330.0,
      "end_time": 643330.0,
      "text": "hasn&#39;t prepared us for what we&#39;re going to need to do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 643330.0,
      "end_time": 646330.0,
      "text": "or who we&#39;re going to need to be."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 646330.0,
      "end_time": 648330.0,
      "text": "We are going to need"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 648330.0,
      "end_time": 653330.0,
      "text": "a new generation of citizen leaders"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 653330.0,
      "end_time": 656330.0,
      "text": "willing to commit ourselves to growing and changing and learning"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 656330.0,
      "end_time": 658330.0,
      "text": "as rapidly as possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 658330.0,
      "end_time": 661330.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s why I have one last thing I want to show you."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 661330.0,
      "end_time": 663330.0,
      "text": "This is a photograph taken about 100 years ago"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 663330.0,
      "end_time": 666330.0,
      "text": "of my grandfather and great-grandfather."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 666330.0,
      "end_time": 669330.0,
      "text": "This is a newspaper publisher and a banker."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 669330.0,
      "end_time": 671330.0,
      "text": "And they were great community leaders."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 671330.0,
      "end_time": 674330.0,
      "text": "And, yes, they were great philanthropists."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 674330.0,
      "end_time": 676330.0,
      "text": "I keep this photograph close by to me --"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 676330.0,
      "end_time": 678330.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s in my office --"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 678330.0,
      "end_time": 681330.0,
      "text": "because I&#39;ve always felt a mystical connection to these two men,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 681330.0,
      "end_time": 684330.0,
      "text": "both of whom I never knew."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 684330.0,
      "end_time": 688330.0,
      "text": "And so, in their honor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 688330.0,
      "end_time": 693330.0,
      "text": "I want to offer you this blank slide."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 693330.0,
      "end_time": 696330.0,
      "text": "And I want you to imagine"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 696330.0,
      "end_time": 699330.0,
      "text": "that this a photograph of you."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 699330.0,
      "end_time": 702330.0,
      "text": "And I want you to think about the community"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 702330.0,
      "end_time": 704330.0,
      "text": "that you want to be part of creating."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 704330.0,
      "end_time": 707330.0,
      "text": "Whatever that means to you."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 707330.0,
      "end_time": 710330.0,
      "text": "And I want you to imagine"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 710330.0,
      "end_time": 713330.0,
      "text": "that it&#39;s 100 years from now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 713330.0,
      "end_time": 717330.0,
      "text": "and your grandchild, or great-grandchild,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 717330.0,
      "end_time": 721330.0,
      "text": "or niece or nephew or god-child,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 721330.0,
      "end_time": 725330.0,
      "text": "is looking at this photograph of you."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 725330.0,
      "end_time": 739330.0,
      "text": "What is the story you most want for them to tell?"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 739330.0,
      "end_time": 741330.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 741330.0,
      "end_time": 747330.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}